  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0baa\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc7 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0ba3\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rani should be taught a better lesson than Gotabaya - People's Liberation Front",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is now clear who is the enemy of the people. So the pressure to dissolve the parliament should be continued.",
        "People's Liberation Front (JVP) general secretary Dilvin Silva said Ranil should be taught a better lesson than Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "JVP He stated this at a press conference held at the headquarters on Friday, 22nd.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe has been involved in anti-democratic activities since his inauguration as Prime Minister.",
        "Because of that, there have been attacks on empty-faced demonstrators. Journalists, lawyers and civil activists have been arrested during this.",
        "We strongly condemn these activities. This is a bad situation. These repressions of Ranil should be stopped immediately.",
        "Everyone needs to come together for that. Amid the bloodshed, Ranil Wickremesinghe tries to protect the Rajapaksa family. Ranil did not understand the reality.",
        "Earlier Gotabaya Rajapaksa's attempts to bring about military rule were not successful.",
        "So Ranil Wickremesinghe must understand that he cannot stop the uprising by threatening the people with the army.",
        "It is now clear who is the enemy of the people. It is also known where they are. Therefore, the existing people must continue to exert pressure to dissolve the arbitrary government.",
        "The struggle to oust Ranil Wickremesinghe should also be continued. Ranil should be taught a better lesson than Gotabaya Rajapaksa, he said."
      ],
